---
import type { CoinSnapshot } from '../data/market';
import { heroSummaryFallback, marketMeta } from '../data/market';
import { formatPercent } from '../lib/format';

const { featuredCoin, apiBase = '' } = Astro.props as {
  featuredCoin: CoinSnapshot;
  apiBase?: string;
};
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-compact">
    <div class="hero-topline">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">한국 프리미엄 관측소</div>
        <h1>김프만 보지 말고,<br />한국 시장 전체 프리미엄.</h1>
        <p class="hero-lede">
          스테이블코인, BTC, 국내 거래소 차이, 해외 ETF 괴리율, 원자재 프리미엄을 한 화면에서 비교합니다.
          이 사이트는 매수·매도 신호가 아니라, 한국 가격이 글로벌 기준보다 비싼지 싼지 관측하는 도구입니다.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-badges">
        <div class="lang-badge status-dot" id="hero-live-status" data-state={apiBase ? 'delayed' : 'offline'}>
          {apiBase ? '연결 준비 중' : `스냅샷 · ${marketMeta.updatedAt}`}
        </div>
        <div class="lang-badge">{marketMeta.cacheWindowSeconds}초 캐시</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-cta-row" role="tablist" aria-label="대시보드 탭">
      <button type="button" class="hero-cta hero-cta-primary" data-tab="premium" role="tab" aria-selected="true">
        한국 프리미엄 보기
      </button>
      <button type="button" class="hero-cta" data-tab="risk" role="tab" aria-selected="false">
        위험 신호 보기
      </button>
      <button type="button" class="hero-cta" data-tab="etf" role="tab" aria-selected="false">
        ETF 괴리율 보기
      </button>
      <button type="button" class="hero-cta" data-tab="data" role="tab" aria-selected="false">
        데이터 기준 보기
      </button>
    </div>

    {/* Tab 1: 한국 프리미엄 (default 6 cards, 2x3) */}
    <div class="summary-grid summary-grid-3col tab-panel active" data-panel="premium" role="tabpanel">
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary">
        <strong>USDT 김프</strong>
        <span id="summary-usdt-premium" class="positive">{heroSummaryFallback.usdtLabel}</span>
        <p>업비트 KRW-USDT vs 1달러 환산</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>USDC 김프</strong>
        <span id="summary-usdc-premium" class="positive">{heroSummaryFallback.usdcLabel}</span>
        <p>업비트 KRW-USDC vs 1달러 환산</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary">
        <strong>코인 한국/해외</strong>
        <span id="summary-global-premium" class={featuredCoin.premiumPercent >= 0 ? 'positive' : 'negative'}>
          BTC {formatPercent(featuredCoin.premiumPercent)}
        </span>
        <p>업비트 vs 바이낸스</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>코인 국내 거래소 차이</strong>
        <span id="summary-domestic-premium" class={featuredCoin.domesticSpreadPercent >= 0 ? 'positive' : 'negative'}>
          BTC {formatPercent(featuredCoin.domesticSpreadPercent)}
        </span>
        <p>업비트 vs 빗썸</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>ETF 괴리율</strong>
        <span id="summary-etf-deviation" class={heroSummaryFallback.etfLeadLabel.includes('-') ? 'negative' : 'positive'}>
          {heroSummaryFallback.etfLeadLabel}
        </span>
        <p>국내 상장 해외 ETF</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>원자재 프리미엄</strong>
        <span
          id="summary-commodity-premium"
          class={heroSummaryFallback.commodityLeadLabel.includes('-') ? 'negative' : 'positive'}
        >
          {heroSummaryFallback.commodityLeadLabel}
        </span>
        <p>금 · 은 · 구리 · 원유</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    {/* Tab 2: 위험 신호 (8 cards in 2x4 layout via 4-col grid) */}
    <div class="summary-grid summary-grid-4col tab-panel" data-panel="risk" role="tabpanel" hidden>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary">
        <strong>KIMP Index</strong>
        <span id="hero-risk-kimp">+0.06%</span>
        <p id="hero-risk-kimp-label">정상</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary">
        <strong>코인 F&G (Crypto)</strong>
        <span id="hero-risk-fg-coin">26</span>
        <p id="hero-risk-fg-coin-label">Fear</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary">
        <strong>미국증시 F&G (CNN)</strong>
        <span id="hero-risk-fg-cnn">47</span>
        <p id="hero-risk-fg-cnn-label">Neutral</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>USD/KRW</strong>
        <span id="hero-risk-usdkrw">1478.99</span>
        <p>환율 스트레스</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>BTC 한국/해외</strong>
        <span id="hero-risk-btc-global">+0.05%</span>
        <p>대표 코인 프리미엄</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>BTC 국내 거래소</strong>
        <span id="hero-risk-btc-domestic">+0.01%</span>
        <p>한국 내부 수급</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>BTC 펀딩비</strong>
        <span id="hero-risk-btc-funding">+0.0100%</span>
        <p>선물 포지션 쏠림</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>BTC OI 24h</strong>
        <span id="hero-risk-btc-oi">+1.20%</span>
        <p>청산 대리지표</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    {/* Tab 3: ETF 괴리율 — top 6 by abs deviation (live wired in index.astro) */}
    <div class="summary-grid summary-grid-3col tab-panel" data-panel="etf" role="tabpanel" hidden>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary" data-etf-slot="0">
        <strong class="etf-name">데이터 로드 중…</strong>
        <span class="etf-dev">-</span>
        <p class="etf-bench">국내 상장 해외 ETF</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary" data-etf-slot="1">
        <strong class="etf-name">-</strong>
        <span class="etf-dev">-</span>
        <p class="etf-bench">-</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary" data-etf-slot="2">
        <strong class="etf-name">-</strong>
        <span class="etf-dev">-</span>
        <p class="etf-bench">-</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card" data-etf-slot="3">
        <strong class="etf-name">-</strong>
        <span class="etf-dev">-</span>
        <p class="etf-bench">-</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card" data-etf-slot="4">
        <strong class="etf-name">-</strong>
        <span class="etf-dev">-</span>
        <p class="etf-bench">-</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card" data-etf-slot="5">
        <strong class="etf-name">-</strong>
        <span class="etf-dev">-</span>
        <p class="etf-bench">-</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    {/* Tab 4: 데이터 기준 — static methodology */}
    <div class="summary-grid summary-grid-3col tab-panel" data-panel="data" role="tabpanel" hidden>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary">
        <strong>코인</strong>
        <span class="data-source">Upbit · Bithumb · Binance</span>
        <p>거래대금 가중. 환율 Frankfurter USD/KRW. 캐시 3초.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary">
        <strong>ETF / 원자재</strong>
        <span class="data-source">K-ETF · Stooq</span>
        <p>국내 상장 해외 ETF의 시장가 vs NAV 괴리. 벤치마크는 GLD/SLV/CPER 등.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card summary-card-primary">
        <strong>심리 지표</strong>
        <span class="data-source">alternative.me · CNN</span>
        <p>코인은 alternative.me Fear&amp;Greed, 미국 주식은 CNN dataviz.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>BTC 선물</strong>
        <span class="data-source">Binance Futures</span>
        <p>펀딩비(8h) + 미결제약정 24h 변화.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>업데이트 주기</strong>
        <span class="data-source">3초 / 1분 / 5분</span>
        <p>코인 3초, F&amp;G·환율 1분, CNN 5분 캐시.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="summary-card">
        <strong>방법론 전체</strong>
        <span class="data-source"><a class="text-link" href="/methodology">/methodology</a></span>
        <p>데이터 출처·계산식·면책 사항 한 페이지로 정리.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-cta { cursor: pointer; }
  .tab-panel[hidden] { display: none !important; }
  .summary-grid-4col { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  /* 모바일에서는 4열도 2열로 자연 reflow (global.css 의 ≤960px 이미 처리됨) */
  .data-source { font-size: 1.05rem !important; }
</style>

<script>
  (function () {
    const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.hero-cta-row [data-tab]');
    const panels = document.querySelectorAll('[data-panel]');
    if (!tabs.length || !panels.length) return;

    function activate(tabKey: string) {
      tabs.forEach((btn) => {
        const isActive = btn.getAttribute('data-tab') === tabKey;
        btn.classList.toggle('hero-cta-primary', isActive);
        btn.setAttribute('aria-selected', isActive ? 'true' : 'false');
      });
      panels.forEach((panel) => {
        const match = panel.getAttribute('data-panel') === tabKey;
        if (match) {
          panel.removeAttribute('hidden');
          panel.classList.add('active');
        } else {
          panel.setAttribute('hidden', '');
          panel.classList.remove('active');
        }
      });
    }

    tabs.forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const key = btn.getAttribute('data-tab');
        if (key) activate(key);
      });
    });
  })();
</script>
